Checklist for New Release
--------------------------
1. Run create_release

2. Upload to sourceforge.net
   a) indimail-{version}.tar.gz
   b) INSTALL-{version}
   c) INSTALL-MYSQL-{version}
   d) INSTALL-RPM-{version}
   e) README-{version}
   e) indimail-{version}-rpmlintrc
   f) indimail-{version}.spec
   g) ChangeLog
   h) .deb, .rpm

3. Create Release on Sourceforge.net
   a) Add all uploaded files using FRS
   b) Edit Changelog/Release Notes
   c) Edit Instructions for Default, Mac, Linux
   d) Edit download page for Default, Mac, Linux

4. Upload to OpenSUSE
   a) indimail-{version}-rpmlintrc
   b) indimail.spec (after chaning build_on_obs to true)
   c) indimail-{version}.tar.gz

5) News at sourceforge.net
   indimail, indimail-announce on groups.google.com
   Freshmeat announcement ---> twitter (indimail)
   facebook announce ---> twitter (indimail) announce
   twitter announce (cprogrammer)
   indimail microblog announce
   linkedin announce
   https://www.ohloh.net/p/indimail
   technorati
   edit release info on en.wikepedia, sourceforge mediawiki
   close all feature requests which got introduced with this
   release

6. Increment version
   1) configure.in
   2) rename indimail source directory
   3) edit file RELEASE
   4) edit ChangeLog and put entry for the new release
